values: This journal is the dream journal of <lj user=kiikii_usagi>. If you would like to read the strangeness, then send me a comment and tell me who you are. If I know you, I'll add to my friends list here so you can read them. Be forewarned, though, my dreams are very scattered and often don't make much sense, and they seem to get even stranger when I attempt recounting them. That is all.
